+# [PATCH 0029 / #6 item 1] async /config switch state. The model swap can take
+# minutes (uncached-model download), blowing a synchronous client's read timeout.
+# With ?wait=false the switch runs on a background thread, /config returns 202,
+# and this state is surfaced in GET /queue.config_switch so the client polls.
+_config_switch_lock = threading.Lock()
